# boxboxboard  — iRacing Season Planner
## Environment Configuration

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# .env.local — NEVER commit this file
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# iRacing API base (should not change)
IRACING_API_BASE=https://members-ng.iracing.com

# App secret for session signing (generate a random 32-char string)
# Generate with: openssl rand -hex 32
NEXTAUTH_SECRET=your_super_secret_here_generate_with_openssl_rand_hex_32

# Your app's public URL (no trailing slash)
NEXTAUTH_URL=http://localhost:3000

# Optional: Supabase for persistent favorites (instead of localStorage)
# SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project.supabase.co
# SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your_anon_key

# Optional: Redis for API response caching
# REDIS_URL=redis://localhost:6379

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# README — SETUP & RUN
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# 1. Install dependencies
#    npm install

# 2. Copy env template
#    cp .env.example .env.local
#    (then fill in your values)

# 3. Run development server
#    npm run dev

# 4. Open http://localhost:3000

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# iRACING API NOTES
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Auth endpoint: POST https://members-ng.iracing.com/auth
# Body: { "email": "...", "password": "..." }
# Returns: { authcode, custId, ... } + sets session cookies
#
# All /data/* endpoints require the session cookie from auth.
# The proxy in /app/api/iracing/[...route]/route.ts forwards cookies automatically.
#
# S3 redirect pattern:
#   Many endpoints return { "link": "https://..." } pointing to S3.
#   The proxy handles this transparently by following the redirect.
#
# Rate limits:
#   iRacing doesn't publish exact limits but be conservative:
#   - Don't exceed 1 req/200ms (built into proxy)
#   - Cache responses for 1h where possible
#   - Batch requests where possible
#
# Key endpoints used:
#   POST /auth                           → Login
#   GET  /data/series/seasons            → All series for a season
#   GET  /data/series/assets             → Series logos/backgrounds  
#   GET  /data/season/list               → Available seasons
#   GET  /data/cars                      → All cars list
#   GET  /data/track/list                → All tracks list
#   GET  /data/carclass/list             → Car classes
#   GET  /data/member/info               → Current user info
#   GET  /data/member/assets             → Owned cars/tracks

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# ⚠️ LEGAL / TOS WARNINGS
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# 1. iRacing TOS: You must comply with iRacing's Terms of Service.
#    This app is for personal use / fan project only.
#    Do NOT use this for commercial purposes without iRacing's permission.
#
# 2. API Rate Limiting: Respect iRacing's servers.
#    Implement caching (default 1h TTL) and don't hammer the API.
#    The proxy includes a 200ms minimum delay between requests.
#
# 3. Credentials: Never log or store user passwords.
#    The proxy passes credentials directly to iRacing without storing them.
#
# 4. Data freshness: Season schedules update weekly.
#    Cache for 1 hour max; use stale-while-revalidate for good UX.
#
# 5. This app is NOT affiliated with or endorsed by iRacing.com Motorsport Simulations, LLC.
